    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, budget-friendly option for daily commuting. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few minor door dings, and some clear coat peeling on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and a few stains, though all electronics and the air conditioning are still functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new brake pads or tires in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
