    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to look at my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and it shows\u2014she truly looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor. Always tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and treated with nothing but the best care. You might find a tiny, nearly invisible pebble mark if you use a magnifying glass, but otherwise, she\u2019s a total dream. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate her as much as I have. Give me a shout and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This specimen represents the zenith of mechanical refinement. The powertrain has been meticulously optimized for thermal efficiency, featuring a valvetrain with zero audible lash and a blueprinted induction system that ensures immediate throttle response. The chassis exhibits peak torsional rigidity, with every suspension bushing inspected to meet original factory tolerances for maximum lateral stability. The gear synchronization is buttery smooth, benefiting from a high-performance synthetic fluid flush, while the ECU mapping delivers a perfectly linear power band. This is a turn-key precision instrument, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and finished with a multi-stage ceramic coating for a concours-level aesthetic.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Showroom floor quality. Zero flaws. Mechanically perfect. Lowest price on the market. Won't last the hour. Cash only.",
