    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive poetry. This Midnight Sapphire coupe isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a time capsule of elegance. The leather interior carries the faint, nostalgic scent of a private library, while the engine hums with the disciplined grace of a cello in a grand hall. Every curve of its hand-polished silhouette captures the moonlight, whispering stories of coastal drives and sunset horizons. This is a rare opportunity to own a piece of rolling art that feels less like a machine and more like a soulmate for the open road.",
      "price": 48900.0,
